Josie Cunningham is a lot of things – but she proved she's a woman of her word tonight. 
Over the weekend she promised fans she'd show "how well your taxes were spent" by sharing a topless photo if her post got 100 retweets. 
And tonight, the 26 year old kept her word and shared a topless snap. 
Josie entered the public eye in 2009 after having a boob job on the NHS. 
And the fame-hungry star also shared a link to her Amazon wish list – promising a hi-res image to whoever buys her a present. Josie Cunningham was once dubbed Britain's most hated woman (Photo: Sunday Mirror) 
"Whoever buys me pressies, DM details and I'll send high res #GodblessTheNHS," she tweeted. 
The wishlist includes risque items such as a leather chastity belt and an 'I Love My Dildo' T-shirt. 
It also includes more practical items such as a £3,529 fridge freezer and £689 sofa. 
Just last week Josie revealed she has a new 65-year-old 'sugar daddy' who's showering her with gifts. 
She claims the pensioner has shelled out for a Swarovski watch, top-of-the-range cordless vacuum cleaner, flatscreen TVs and even beds to furnish her home.
